edBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T17:43:38.000Z","msg":"我係睇情況，如果夜晚/放假先揸車過嚟海"},{"pid":"35d10fc66d255fc582a9f06c71420fbdf9b09b81","tid":2288333,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T17:46:44.000Z","msg":"去一個區, 都可能會揸車. <br />\n如果要去幾多區, 會坐車<br />\n成日行街都太子&gt;旺角&gt;油麻地&gt;尖沙咀...你叫我返轉頭攞車, 攞得嚟我都差唔多返到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33474cbc7a2de1f17025b5f2d71a85f91a9b2a7","tid":2288333,"uid":14054,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T18:00:19.000Z","msg":"其實香港揸車都唔係為咗快，<br />\n想慳時間而揸嘅勸你可以搭返巴士地鐵<br />\n本身買車都係諗住做holiday driver<br />\n點知一返真係返唔到轉頭<br />\n個私人空間嘅感覺好正<br />\n同搭的士uber唔同<br />\n想佢揸慢啲行咩路冷氣開幾大唔洗同司機講 自己話哂事<br />\n有人冇乜所謂，但我就係嗰啲毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己本身又唔係成日趕時間做呢樣做嗰樣<br />\n揸車fit哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bc2ac04f244e2903a87f2f0f104041dc1ce0ba","tid":2288333,"uid":6778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T18:24:40.000Z","msg":"成兩年沒坐過巴士黨鐵,  要車人就渣46,  去旺區 番工就渣26   諗番起以前同人迫鐵迫巴士 沒位坐 企成個鐘就想嘔"},{"pid":"baf36f5e69bc92a7b58d7a672fadb4d6dfd015b6","tid":2288333,"uid":191211,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T18:36:53.000Z","msg":"weekdays 無論去邊都揸<br />\nweekend 就 staycation 唔揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f1f99765a207324a9b680796a869e9a1acd060","tid":2288333,"uid":69864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b2add6c5e7f3fc7ba256587bcabed6b3431e69ba","tid":2288333,"uid":157483,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46295a369c8bb997dd994bf93a9cf5d9c4e450fa","tid":2288333,"uid":69864,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:42:42.000Z","msg":"我係一個月坐60次以上的士同uber 既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明你感受，但係我連自己渣都懶，<br />\n又要搵地方泊，又要自己渣冇得休息<br />\n所以啲錢最後比司機賺算"},"citedBy":1,"